TITLE: Implementing PeerListAck Message for Peer Acknowledgment
DESCRIPTION: The PeerListAck message is sent in response to PeerList to acknowledge the subset of peers that the peer will attempt to connect to.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/api-reference/standards/avalanche-network-protocol.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_5

