TITLE: Defining Unit Tests for Precompile Functions in Go
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines a set of unit tests for precompile functions including 'add', 'nextTwo', and 'repeat'. It tests both insufficient gas scenarios and correct function outputs. The tests are structured using a map of testutils.PrecompileTest objects.
