TITLE: Generating BIP39 Mnemonic with AvalancheJS
DESCRIPTION: Creates a 256-bit strength 24-word English mnemonic phrase using AvalancheJS library. This mnemonic can be used to derive hierarchical deterministic wallets.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/dapps/end-to-end/fuji-workflow.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { Mnemonic } from "avalanche";
const mnemonic: Mnemonic = Mnemonic.getInstance();
