SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/guides/telegram-miniapps-thirdweb.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
 <TransactionButton\n    transaction={() => {\n        const transaction = prepareTransaction({\n        to: avaxRecipient,\n        chain: avalancheFuji,\n        client: client,\n        value: toWei(avaxAmount),\n    });\n    return transaction;\n    }}\n    onTransactionConfirmed={() => { console.log(\"Transaction confirmed\") }}\n    onError={() => { console.log(\"Transaction error\") }}\n    >\n    Confirm Transaction\n</TransactionButton>
```

