TITLE: Specifying NFT Transfer Output Structure in Text Format
DESCRIPTION: Gantt chart representation of the NFT Transfer Output binary format, showing field types, sizes, and the total size calculation. This specification details how NFT Transfer Output data is structured in memory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/api-reference/x-chain/txn-format.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
+-----------+------------+-------------------------------+
| type_id   : int        |                       4 bytes |
+-----------+------------+-------------------------------+
| group_id  : int        |                       4 bytes |
+-----------+------------+-------------------------------+
| payload   : []byte     |        4 + len(payload) bytes |
+-----------+------------+-------------------------------+
| locktime  : long       |                       8 bytes |
+-----------+------------+-------------------------------+
| threshold : int        |                       4 bytes |
+-----------+------------+-------------------------------+
| addresses : [][20]byte | 4 + 20 * len(addresses) bytes |
+-----------+------------+-------------------------------+
                         |             28 + len(payload) |
                         |  + 20 * len(addresses) bytes  |
                         +-------------------------------+
```

