TITLE: Defining State Structure in TimestampVM (Rust)
DESCRIPTION: The State struct definition that maintains the blockchain state for TimestampVM. It contains a database for storing accepted blocks and a hashmap for tracking verified but not yet accepted blocks. Both are wrapped in Arc and RwLock for concurrent access.
