TITLE: Implementing Avalanche Consensus Algorithm in Pseudo-code
DESCRIPTION: This pseudo-code snippet illustrates the Avalanche consensus algorithm. It demonstrates the process of querying other validators, changing preferences based on responses, and finalizing decisions after consecutive successes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/academy/avalanche-fundamentals/02-avalanche-consensus-intro/03-snowman-consensus.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: pseudo
CODE:
```
preferredValue = initialPreference()
consecutiveSuccesses = 0

while consecutiveSuccesses < β do
    responses = sample(k)
    if !isPreferred(preferredValue, responses, α) then
        preferredValue = majorityValue(responses)
        consecutiveSuccesses = 0
    else
        consecutiveSuccesses += 1
    end if
end while

accept(preferredValue)
```

