TITLE: Gantt Format Specification for Unsigned Add Delegator TX
DESCRIPTION: A structured layout diagram showing the byte structure of an unsigned add delegator transaction, including its components: BaseTx, Validator, Stake, and RewardsOwner, with their respective sizes.
