CODE:
```
message AddPermissionlessDelegatorTx {
    BaseTx base_tx = 1;         // size(base_tx)
    Validator validator = 2;    // size(validator)
    SubnetID subnet_id = 3;     // 32 bytes
    repeated TransferOut stake_outs = 4; // 4 bytes + size(stake_outs)
