TITLE: Calculating Validator Reward in Avalanche Network using LaTeX
DESCRIPTION: This LaTeX formula calculates the reward for a responsive validator in the Avalanche network based on stake amount, staking period, and network parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/nodes/validate/how-to-stake.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: latex
CODE:
```
