TITLE: Unsigned Export TX Structure Specification in Avalanche X-Chain
DESCRIPTION: Gantt and Protocol Buffer specifications for the Unsigned Export TX format, which includes BaseTx, DestinationChain, and an array of Transferable Outputs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/api-reference/x-chain/txn-format.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_41

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
+-------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------+
| base_tx           : BaseTx        |                  size(base_tx) bytes |
+-------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------+
| destination_chain : [32]byte      |                             32 bytes |
+-------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------+
| outs              : []TransferOut |                 4 + size(outs) bytes |
+-------------------+---------------+--------------------------------------+
                          | 36 + size(outs) + size(base_tx) bytes |
                          +---------------------------------------+
```

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
message ExportTx {
    BaseTx base_tx = 1;            // size(base_tx)
    bytes destination_chain = 2;   // 32 bytes
    repeated TransferOut outs = 3; // 4 bytes + size(outs)
}
```

