+--------------+-------------+------------------------------------------+
| subnet_auth  : SubnetAuth  |                  size(subnet_auth) bytes |
+--------------+-------------+------------------------------------------+
               | 74 + size(base_tx) + size(chain_name) + size(fx_ids) + |
