TITLE: Defining GenesisAsset Structure in Protocol Buffers for Avalanche
DESCRIPTION: This specification details the GenesisAsset structure using Protocol Buffers format, listing all fields with their data types and byte sizes. It provides a more modern representation of the same structure defined in the Gantt format.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/api-reference/x-chain/txn-format.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_54

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
message GenesisAsset {
    string alias = 1;                          // 2 bytes + len(alias)
    uint32 network_id = 2;                     // 04 bytes
    bytes blockchain_id = 3;                   // 32 bytes
    repeated Output outputs = 4;               // 04 bytes + size(outputs)
    repeated Input inputs = 5;                 // 04 bytes + size(inputs)
    bytes memo = 6;                            // 04 bytes + size(memo)
    string name = 7;                           // 2 bytes + len(name)
    name symbol = 8;                           // 2 bytes + len(symbol)
    uint8 denomination = 9;                    // 1 bytes
    repeated InitialState initial_states = 10; // 4 bytes + size(initial_states)
}
```

