TITLE: Computing Effective Consumption Rate for Avalanche Staking Rewards
DESCRIPTION: This LaTeX formula calculates the Effective Consumption Rate used in determining validator rewards, based on minimum and maximum consumption rates and staking period.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/nodes/validate/how-to-stake.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: latex
CODE:
```
EffectiveConsumptionRate = 
\frac{MinConsumptionRate}{PercentDenominator} \times \left(1- \frac{Staking Period}{Minting Period}\right) + \frac{MaxConsumptionRate}{PercentDenominator} \times \frac{Staking Period}{Minting Period}
```

