TITLE: Defining Transferable Op with Proto Specification
DESCRIPTION: Protocol buffer message specifications for UTXOID and TransferableOp. The UTXOID contains a tx_id and utxo_index, while TransferableOp includes an asset_id, an array of UTXOIDs, and a transfer_op.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/api-reference/x-chain/txn-format.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
message UTXOID {
    bytes tx_id = 1;       // 32 bytes
    uint32 utxo_index = 2; // 04 bytes
}
message TransferableOp {
    bytes asset_id = 1;           // 32 bytes
    repeated UTXOID utxo_ids = 2; // 4 + 36 * len(utxo_ids) bytes
    TransferOp transfer_op = 3;   // size(transfer_op)
}
```

