TITLE: Calculating Effective Consumption Rate in LaTeX
DESCRIPTION: This LaTeX formula calculates the Effective Consumption Rate, which determines the reward rate based on the staking period selection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/quick-start/rewards-formula.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: latex
CODE:
```
EffectiveConsumptionRate =
\frac{MinConsumptionRate}{PercentDenominator} \times \left(1- \frac{Staking Period}{Minting Period}\right) + \frac{MaxConsumptionRate}{PercentDenominator} \times \frac{Staking Period}{Minting Period}
```

