TITLE: Defining SECP256K1 Mint Output Structure in Text
DESCRIPTION: Specifies the structure of a SECP256K1 Mint output using a Gantt-style diagram. It shows the byte layout for TypeID, Locktime, Threshold, and Addresses fields.
