TITLE: Adding Avalanche Network to MetaMask
DESCRIPTION: Function to programmatically add the Avalanche network to MetaMask using the wallet_addEthereumChain method via web3 provider.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/docs/dapps/advanced-tutorials/add-network-programmatically.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
function addAvalancheNetwork() {
  injected.getProvider().then((provider) => {
    provider
      .request({
        method: "wallet_addEthereumChain",
        params: [AVALANCHE_MAINNET_PARAMS],
      })
      .catch((error: any) => {
        console.log(error);
      });
  });
}
```

