TITLE: X-Chain Transaction Fee Schedule
DESCRIPTION: A table showing the fixed transaction fees for different operation types on Avalanche's X-Chain. Fees are denominated in AVAX and vary by transaction type with operations like asset creation costing more than standard transfers.
