LANGUAGE: plaintext
CODE:
```
+----------+---------------------------+--------------------------------+
| Chain    | Transaction Type          | Mainnet Transaction Fee (AVAX) |
+----------+---------------------------+--------------------------------+
| X        | Send                      |                          0.001 |
+----------+---------------------------+--------------------------------+
| X        | Create Asset              |                           0.01 |
+----------+---------------------------+--------------------------------+
| X        | Mint Asset                |                          0.001 |
+----------+---------------------------+--------------------------------+
| X        | Import AVAX               |                          0.001 |
