TITLE: Creating a Styled Telegram Community Link Button in React
DESCRIPTION: Creates a styled anchor element that links to the Avalanche Academy Telegram community. The button uses the cn utility to apply button variants with a large size.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ava-labs/builders-hub.git/blob/master/content/common/intro/course-chat.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
<a
    href="https://t.me/avalancheacademy"
    target='_blank'
    className={cn(buttonVariants({ size: 'lg' }))}
>
    Join Telegram Course Chat
</a>
```
